#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_smithing_table/init.lua:36
msgid "Upgrade Gear"
msgstr "升级装备"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_smithing_table/init.lua:135
msgid "Smithing Table"
msgstr "锻造台"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_smithing_table/init.lua:136
msgid ""
"A smithing table is a utility block used to alter tools and armor at the "
"cost of a smithing template and the appropriate material. This is the only "
"way to obtain trimmed armor or upgrade diamond equipment with netherite. It "
"also serves as a toolsmith's job site block."
msgstr ""
"锻造台是一种实用方块，可用于改造工具和盔甲，不过需要消耗锻造模板以及相应的材"
"料。这是获得纹饰盔甲或用下界合金升级钻石装备的唯一途径。它还可用作工具匠的工"
"作站点方块。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_smithing_table/init.lua:137
msgid ""
"Rightclick on a smithing table to access its interface. Put armor or tools "
"in the upper left slot. The top right slot is reserved for mineral items. "
"The bottom slot is for smithing templates. To upgrade your diamond armor and "
"tools to netherite, the netherite upgrade template is required."
msgstr ""
"右键点击锻造台可进入其操作界面。将盔甲或工具放入左上角的插槽。右上角的插槽预"
"留给矿物类物品。下方的插槽用于放置锻造模板。若要将你的钻石盔甲和工具升级为下"
"界合金制品，就需要下界合金升级模板。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_smithing_table/init.lua:138
msgid ""
"To trim your armor, you need a mineral item and a smithing template. Each "
"piece of armor can be given an trimming pattern. The items are consumed "
"after trimming and the armor piece receives the pattern defined by the "
"template."
msgstr ""
"要给你的盔甲添加纹饰，你需要一件矿物类物品和一个锻造模板。每件盔甲都可以被赋"
"予一种纹饰图案。这些物品在添加纹饰后会被消耗，而盔甲部件则会获得由模板所定义"
"的图案。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_smithing_table/init.lua:139
msgid ""
"List of mineral items:\n"
"• Amethyst Shard\n"
"• Copper Ingot\n"
"• Diamond\n"
"• Emerald\n"
"• Gold Ingot\n"
"• Iron Ingot\n"
"• Lapis Lazuli\n"
"• Netherite Ingot\n"
"• Quartz\n"
"• Redstone"
msgstr ""
"矿物类物品清单：\n"
"• 紫水晶碎片\n"
"• 铜锭\n"
"• 钻石\n"
"• 绿宝石\n"
"• 金锭\n"
"• 铁锭\n"
"• 青金石\n"
"• 下界合金锭\n"
"• 石英\n"
"• 红石"
